Chiril Covalciuc (Ukrainian:  ; born 11 June 1986), nicknamed Tom Cruise, is a Moldovan-Ukrainian professional footballer who currently plays for FC Chornomorets Odesa in the Ukrainian Premier League. He made his debut in the Russian Premier League for FC Tom Tomsk on July 19, 2009 in a game against FC Khimki.[1] Serghei Covalciuc, also a footballer playing for Chornomorets, is his elder brother. 
